00Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/164335_4c9bdee1fbf2b820ce0bf54ff2fb513c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F164335_4c9bdee1fbf2b820ce0bf54ff2fb513c.png&h=dfd0b809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d47e022e0e35b4df81026796191674694e445138","tid":806866,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de15a523ed1bcbbe0475331f45583b8eb4e474d1","tid":806866,"uid":61280,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-pacific-forum-china/nauru-blasts-insolent-china-for-speaking-out-of-turn-at-meeting-idUSKCN1LL0AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-pacific-forum-china%2Fnauru-blasts-insolent-china-for-speaking-out-of-turn-at-meeting-idUSKCN1LL0AC&d=uBYJM3W7FLnsvUVMBqqPe4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e7c4c769\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-pacific-forum-china%2Fnauru-blasts-insolent-china-for-speaking-out-of-turn-at-meeting-idUSKCN1LL0AC&h=2044748d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-pacific-forum-china/nauru-blasts-insolent-china-for-speaking-out-of-turn-at-meeting-idUSKCN1LL0AC</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單野路透社開頭就用&quot;insolent&quot; and &quot;bully&quot;去形容中國既舉動，係我覺得好少有既<br />\n<br />\n近年中國對太平洋島國大肆注資，成為該區第二大注資國，威脅到澳洲、新西蘭既權益，所以澳洲響會中提出要中國按照澳洲一直以黎既規矩，亦導致中國今次發爛渣瘋狂搶咪<br />\n<br />\n其他島國如薩摩亞、斐濟因為獲中國投資而反對，並威脅瑙魯要退出論壇，所以見到中國除左薩爾瓦多，仲開始伸手威脅南島世界<br />\n<br />\n美、澳洲、新西蘭既對抗並非無道理</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那已經開始放狗，今日支支TVB81台83台不斷loop新西蘭浪費公帑HK$41萬為自己個BB搭飛機，幾撚大新聞呀！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報美帝大板新西蘭etc多多墨水，支那粵東大水災湖南暴動就一滴都冇！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.